<div class="user-guide-page container">
  <h1><%= page.title %></h1>
  <p class="lead"><%= page.description %></p>

  <div class="guide-screenshot mb-4">
    <img src="<%= page.screenshotUrl %>" alt="<%= page.title %> screenshot" class="img-fluid border" />
  </div>

  <h2>Club profile and administration</h2>
  <p>Use this area to update your club's public profile, contact information, and images.</p>

  <h3>Editing club information</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Navigate to <a href="/clubs">Clubs</a> and find your club, or use the Admin &gt; Clubs menu.</li>
    <li>Click <em>Edit</em> next to your club to update name, description, meeting details and social links.</li>
    <li>Click <em>Save</em> to persist changes.</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Uploading logos and images</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Click <em>Upload Logo</em> to select an image file (PNG, JPG).</li>
    <li>Ensure the file meets size and dimension recommendations to display correctly across the site.</li>
    <li>After uploading, use the provided preview and save the profile.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-3"><a href="<%= page.url %>">Open the Club Management page</a></p>
  <p><a href="/user-guide">Back to guide index</a></p>
</div>
